-- 
N.Z. Publishes Renewable Power Policy Statement to Encourage Investments

-- B y   T r a c y   W i t h e r s
-- 
2011-04-12T05:22:39Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-12/n-z-publishes-renewable-power-policy-statement-to-encourage-investments.html
New Zealand  published a National
Policy Statement on renewable electricity generation, aiming to
encourage greater investment in power from wind, hydro,
geothermal and tidal resources. The statement requires local
councils to recognize the importance of renewable generation in
their decision on new projects, Environment Minister Nick Smith
said in an e-mailed statement.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Tracy Withers at 
 twithers@bloomberg.net  